data.description: Beautiful home in desirable Linwood Farms. Spacious porch,crown molding in foyer & formal dining room,open light floor plan main level,office/library w/french doors,kitchen features granite countertops,corian,& tile backsplash, 42 inch cabinets,stainless appliances, gas stove,spacious dining area. Main level bedroom& full bath,small area potential drop zone from garage. Stacked stoned gas fireplace w/switch, tile hearth & cedar mantle. Blinds throughout. Owners retreat w/trey ceilings, garden tub, separate shower, & oversized double walk-in closets.Gentlemen height cabinets in upper bathrooms. Large bonus room, various purposes, personal project workspace, playroom, media room, exercise. Work room w/potential enclosure. Entertain guests privately w/a wooded area, fenced backyard, & extensive stoned patio w/ stoned fire-pit. Storage building to stay. Laundry room upper level w/ folding space. Pull down attic. Excellent community pool & playground area w/ ample parking. Welcome home!
